

Installation : 
Install PECL extension php-yaml :
sudo apt install php-yaml

Preparation :
- Copy config.yml.dist to config.yml
- Adapt the values to your machine

Retrieve the biographies on your local machine :
php step1.php
php step2.php
php step3.php

Execution result :

step 1
permits to retrieve 2842 persons

step 2
permits to retrieve birthplaces except for 166 mathematicians
(1269 birthplaces)




